            {
                "category": "summary",
                "text": "NVIDIA has released a software update for NVIDIA\u00ae Jetson AGX Orin Series and IGX Orin. To protect your system, download and install the latest NVIDIA JetPack SDK from <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/embedded/downloads\">NVIDIA DevZone</a> and the new IGX Orin update from <a href=\"https://developer.nvidia.com/igx-downloads\">IGX Download Center</a>.",
